\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces One representative image per digit from the training fold. Digit~1 exhibits the most uniform stroke pattern; digits 3, 5, and 8 share curved overlapping structure, motivating the 3\,vs.\,8 binary task in Part~C.}}{1}{figure.1}\protected@file@percent }
